<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>01</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>‖ 精致茶饮，纯手工调配无添加 ‖</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200831/3ae534e12ca74c7fa46ce736310f4b0c.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">一杯好的茶饮除了能拿得出手的颜值，味道也相当重要！闲至cafe的茶饮坚持纯手工调配，<strong>新鲜柠檬加上现泡青茶</strong>，带来更清爽的感受！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200831/9535fc56b5b44f8eb81bdb1d65ab2c13.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200831/f4f4bbc42def4027880252d590009828.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">除了8款茶饮，还有6款鸡尾酒供顾客选择！最适合与朋友一起小酌一杯！</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>02</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>‖ 小吃+简餐，呆上一天都不会饿 ‖</strong></p>
