<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>『黑松露牛肉碎炒饭』&amp;『芝士牛肉酱宽意面』</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">ข้าวผัดเนื้อแบล็คทรัฟเฟิล &amp; พาสต้าเนื้อชีส</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200831/d00b8867e84d4931bb55001924dc308d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">黑松露做的炒饭，你还没吃过？呐，来这里，吃到你满足为止~</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200831/78edc44e9fa645f9952637cb40a0b3f1.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
