<p class="ql-align-justify">饭后甜点少不了，绵密柔滑的山药泥搭配酸甜果味的蓝莓酱，解腻又开胃~</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200831/00bc60eca213471892e930f2422c42cf.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
